snippet.title: Mika and the Witch's Mountain - Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam wishlist - https://store.steampowered.com/app/1819460/Mika_and_The_Witchs_Mountain

Soar with the wind on your broomstick, deliver packages to your friends, and explore a vibrant sandbox world in a coming of age adventure about an aspiring witch!

Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Steam and Xbox Series X
